title: The Fitness Marshall Bebe Rexha I Got You Dance Cardio Video | POPSUGAR Fitness
text:
The Fitness Marshall Bebe Rexha I Got You Dance Cardio Video This Fitness Marshall's Dance to Bebe Rexha Is So Fun, It's Electric February 23, 2017 11 Shares Chat with us on Facebook Messenger. Learn what's trending across POPSUGAR. 
The new Bebe Rexha song is INSANELY fun, so of course we're dancing our butts off to it with The Fitness Marshall. This song's theme is "casting a love potion on someone to make them fall in love with us," so Caleb's choreography will naturally have some hilariously themed moves (read: gathering and snatching ingredients, including cream cheese . . . and the heart of a llama). 
Our favorite line? "We're missing one ingredient, and that's hair flips." Trust us, you won't be able to stop moving to this song, or listening to it, or laughing at the hilarious coaching. Related:
